Abstract: Provides relative to additional insured coverage under certain oil and gas
agreements.
Proposed law (R.S. 9:2780(H)) codifies the jurisprudential standard for additional insured
coverage under certain oil and gas agreements set forth in Marcel v. Placid Oil Co., 11 F.3d
563 (1994).
